{
  "stem": "19550.7",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But on the other hand, the intellectual who has had political consciousness, had a better chance of mentally surviving it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in a way, become more useful to his fellow prisoners because of that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there are ample examples and proofs of that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my life was that of the millions who went through Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We would-- we were housed in a wooden barrack, were sleeping on wooden pallets with maybe 12.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And eventually, as it became more crowded-- and this would happen in every other camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The physical setup was the same.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They would pile in more than 12 or 15, where you literally couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you did move, the whole 15 had to move and readjust their position.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At one end of the hall, there was a room where usually what they called the blockalteste, the elder of the block and the kapo would be housed, and where there was some administrative procedure maintained.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at the other end, there was a huge kettle or vat, like a metal vat which was-- played the role of a toilet.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All night long, people would be marching to void and, well, which added a pretty pungent odor to-- to the barrack.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In the winter-- and I wasn't there in the winter-- but in other camps, they would have one little tin oven, which sometimes was fired up to provide some heat.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But basically, you know, the heat was provided by the-- however exhausting, however exhausted, the living organism of the human beings who were pressed in.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
